entries.femaleVariant: I will say, that new suit is calling to me. It's eccentric, sure, but in a subtle way.
Snake skin and silver? A lovely combination, timeless. It would certainly suit you.
Hm, Zane says I shouldn't go for anything too loud.
Oh, for heaven's sake...! Buy it, treat yourself. Worst case you give it away. Or throw it out.
Soon enough, semiganic will be out, and you'll be sad you never got a chance to wear it.
